<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Comics-eyal2020.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1572" title="Comics-eyal2020" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Comics-eyal2020.png" alt="" width="435" height="221" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: right;">.</p>
