<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Comics-sapisapi.bmp"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1598" title="Comics-sapisapi" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Comics-sapisapi.bmp" alt="" width="471" height="345" /></a></p>
